docs/packet-schema.md:21:The runtime validator checks required packet artifacts, required JSON fields, core field types, status/outcome enums, event structure, metrics and safety report identity fields, provider audit metadata, and manifest references to existing files. It is useful for local CI and future UI/API adapters while remaining small enough to run without a separate schema engine.
