docs/CURRENT_STATE.md:5:RunForge is currently a local, deterministic, artifact-first engineering harness. It can collect evidence, run bounded checks, classify failures, produce proposal/readiness packets, render packet views, record operator decisions, and preserve handoff/archive evidence. It is not yet a complete Agent OS / Task Factory because it has not proven one end-to-end task run.
